1. Download Ubuntu for your System from Official site/Windows from CD.
2. Use Balena Etcher for burning your images on Pendrive.
If using any USB adapter on your system, install its drivers properly to use WiFi.
3. Install VS Code and enable extensions like live-server, code formatter, etc..
4. Install Node/npm from official source.
5. Install mongodb using the Guide.
https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/tutorial/install-mongodb-on-windows/
Direct download link-> https://www.mongodb.com/download-center/community?jmp=docs
